data.revised_prompt: A lively image of an animated, fluffy, brown monkey sitting comfortably on a thick branch of a tropical tree. The monkey has an expressive face, with sparkly eyes, a small nose, and a wide, grinning mouth. In its human-like hands, the monkey is holding a ripe, yellow banana. It is peeling the banana with a look of sheer delight and anticipation. To make the scene more vibrant, the tree is nestled in a lush, dense rainforest with foliage in hues of bright green and flowers of vivid hues, creating a picturesque background.
